<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1007771-i-read-book-1-many-years-ago-and-loved-it">I read book 1 many years ago and Loved It! Now I want to read book 2 but I&#39;m afraid I will be lost. I remember the basic plot of the first novel but have lost a lot of the details. Will I be lost if I start this second book? Should I re-read the first one again? Or just go for it?! Thanks</a>
</div>
