<span id="freeTextContainer13491084417092526599">Literally in love with the premise for this book series, can&apos;t wait to finish the lot and have an empty pit in my stomach realising it&apos;s all over. In a world where every island represents a different hour of the day, you could stick me at 14:00, basking in my speedos in the afternoon heat and I would read Clive Barker&apos;s books over and over. Onwards &amp; upwards, onto the next one. </span>
